{"tid":1837853,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警每日濫捕市民，見靚女就索。醫護每日拯救病人，要用命去博。到底醫護仲係唔係人命","createTime":"2020-01-23T20:03:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T20:03:04.000Z","uid":303950,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ccb3ff9016b46060ef34635b01723e29a6a7096a","tid":1837853,"uid":303950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T20:03:04.000Z","msg":"黑警OT要洗幾億；醫護OT當買知識。<br />\n黑警新年放長假；醫護新年推床架。<br />\n黑警政府照你；醫護政府不理。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為撚左個面子同權勢，政府高官跟本無當過我地醫護係人，只係守護高官既棋子。<br />\n<br />\n面對不公，滅絕人性既狗，我地唔需要對佢仁慈。<br />\n<br />\n抽到照顧武漢廢人既籤時，個個醫護都頹撚曬。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n錢唔可以買起醫護條命，面對受壓榨既情況，你又會點做？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">【抗暴之戰】料3,000人受傷逾半不敢去急症室 義診醫生悲嘆抗爭者：以性命換公義<br />\n</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20191025/5EFBUHTUOB352WPAPQXVSX3ZFY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191025%2F5EFBUHTUOB352WPAPQXVSX3ZFY%2F&d=3vKtw9Y9osNHyU2tDi1UeJKhd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=18497c7f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191025%2F5EFBUHTUOB352WPAPQXVSX3ZFY%2F&h=a93e9610\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20191025/5EFBUHTUOB352WPAPQXVSX3ZFY/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">【抗暴之戰】最少5名醫生被捕 醫護界轟瘋警反綁義務醫生急救員為「戰爭罪行 不能原諒」</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20191118/QF5KVLNOLNULXDHFBJK32YT2JY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191118%2FQF5KVLNOLNULXDHFBJK32YT2JY%2F&d=3vKtw9Y9osNHyU2tDi1UeJKhd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=d6abec57\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191118%2FQF5KVLNOLNULXDHFBJK32YT2JY%2F&h=694d91ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20191118/QF5KVLNOLNULXDHFBJK32YT2JY/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t2QMwAU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=h